@URL = {{BASE_URL}}/auth/api-keys
@API_KEY_ID = 11111111-1111-1111-1111-111111111111

### List API keys
GET {{URL}}
Authorization: Bearer {{JWT}}

### Create API key
POST {{URL}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{JWT}}

{
  "name": "CI Integration"
}

### Rename API key
PUT {{URL}}/{{API_KEY_ID}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{JWT}}

{
  "name": "CI Integration v2"
}

### Revoke API key
DELETE {{URL}}/{{API_KEY_ID}}
Authorization: Bearer {{JWT}}
